1
00:01:01,719 --> 00:01:05,519
Can't you go a little easier on me?

2
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:08,319
This drug triggers a person's rage.

3
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,799
It's not like I want to!

4
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,760
What could you possibly be angry at me for?

5
00:01:13,599 --> 00:01:14,879
What's your relationship with Yun Xi?

6
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,000
I already told you, didn't I?

7
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,400
We were childhood friends.

8
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,959
Why do I find that so hard to believe?

9
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,840
You hem and haw every time I ask.

10
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:21,680
Qi Zhi!

11
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,159
Ouyang Yan!

12
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,680
Where are you?

13
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:28,879
The chicken farmer!

14
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:29,519
Huh?

15
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:33,400
Women just love jumping to conclusions.

16
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:36,120
So what if I jump to conclusions?

17
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:38,799
What are we to each other
that you get to guess?

18
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,200
I'm the one who wants to hit you.

19
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:46,280
You're clearly using the poison as an excuse!

20
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,159
Exactly.

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,840
I'd hit you even without being poisoned.

22
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:55,239
Royal Brother.

23
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:58,120
I know you waaaay too well.

24
00:01:58,719 --> 00:01:59,480
What do you mean?

25
00:01:59,480 --> 00:01:59,879
Hey.

26
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,439
What a coincidence.

27
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:02,319
I slipped something into your drink too.

28
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,920
My carefully crafted Five-Poison Love Potion.

29
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,519
Within three days,

30
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:07,319
you'll be crying, throwing fits,
and threatening suicide over me.

31
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:08,319
By then,

32
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,800
I won't have to worry about controlling you.

33
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,759
Hmph!

34
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,919
Impossible.

35
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,240
All you can do is hit people.

36
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,000
How could you ever control me?

37
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,520
Hey,

38
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,520
once you fall for a hitter like me,

39
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,479
you'll start hitting people with me!

40
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:19,759
You're still drinking?

41
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:21,759
One cup or two, it's all the same.

42
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,680
Why shouldn't I drink?

43
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,680
Fine.

44
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,800
If we die, we die together.

45
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:25,680
Bring it on!

46
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:34,479
Chicken farmer!

47
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,280
Crown Prince!

48
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,759
*Whimpering*

49
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,840
Chicken farmer!

50
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,919
Crown Prince, Consort Zhen, why are you here?

51
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,240
How did you get in?

52
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,319
I asked around.

53
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,800
The prisoners here are too good at fighting.

54
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,800
No one dares to guard this place.

55
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,199
Why are you hitting me?

56
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:46,319
I've been poisoned.

57
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,360
What poison did you take?

58
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,240
Must-Hit Powder.

59
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,560
Once poisoned, you really want to hit people.

60
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:52,199
Oh.

61
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,240
I didn't know.

62
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,680
He hit me!

63
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,199
Mommy, he hit me!

64
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,719
He hit me first!

65
00:03:00,159 --> 00:03:02,080
He hit me so hard, it really hurts!

66
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:02,919
He hit me!

67
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:03,879
I've got an idea.

68
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,520
Ouyang Yan.

69
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,240
The chicken farmer says Yunxi was his first love.

70
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:08,000
What?

71
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:11,639
Didn't you just say she was your neighbor?

72
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:19,319
The effects of this Hit Powder are terrifying!

73
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,479
I doubt that kick was from the Hit Powder.

74
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,960
I want to hit someone every day now.

75
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,039
You must be behind this.

76
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:27,960
You poisoned me!

77
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,360
What is wrong with you?

78
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:30,800
Don't forget,

79
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,560
I'm the one who saved your life.

80
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:34,759
Ungrateful wretch.

81
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:35,520
Come here!

82
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,280
Hey, hey, hey!

83
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,360
Everyone, come look!

84
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,960
The fake doctor drugged me!

85
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,520
The fake doctor poisoned me!

86
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,960
Who'd dare come here for treatment now?

87
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,360
Everyone, come take a look!

88
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:47,599
Alright, alright.

89
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,280
You win, I give up.

90
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,599
The antidote for the hitting urge.

91
00:03:55,919 --> 00:03:57,719
Hey, that's just one dose!

92
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,039
Zhenzhen.

93
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:01,599
What are you all staring at?

94
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,400
You pretend to be poisoned too.

95
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,000
Come over and ask for another packet.

96
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,840
Stop staring!

97
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,199
Doctor.

98
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,319
One more packet of antidote, please.

99
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,720
You've had money all along? Why didn't you tell me?

100
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,279
Hmm?

101
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,040
Well, you never asked.

102
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,120
Here.

103
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:25,759
This is the antidote.

104
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:27,920
You should've mentioned the money sooner!

105
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,199
From the moment I first saw you,

106
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,199
I used the self-injury ploy,

107
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:44,319
killing with a borrowed knife,
fanning flames, surprise counterattack.

108
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:47,360
After all that, you say my schemes aren't clever enough?

109
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,879
What's wrong with you?

110
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,839
Ridiculous.

111
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:53,680
Without you noticing, I used...

112
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:56,560
going with the flow, turning the tables,
sowing discord, and trapping the prey.

113
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,759
So many schemes.

114
00:04:57,759 --> 00:04:59,040
You dare compete with me?

115
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:01,160
Who's more fit to be emperor than me?

116
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:03,839
Me.

117
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:05,120
Stop arguing.

118
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,639
Being emperor takes more than just schemes.

119
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:11,160
Even someone as foolish as the Crown Prince

120
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,720
learned schemes in Ji City.

121
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,519
But look at the two of you.

122
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,959
You'd even betray your closest friends.

123
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:20,519
How can you ensure you won't betray
the people of this land?

124
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:24,920
In that case,

125
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:27,399
if you promise not to fight me for the throne,

126
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,199
I might consider sparing you.

127
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:33,199
If you become emperor and don't come after me,

128
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,279
I'll spare you too.

129
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,000
Deal.

130
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:36,240
The antidote.

131
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,920
Hand it over.

132
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:42,000
You first.

133
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,519
Together.

134
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:44,879
One.

135
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,639
Two.

136
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:46,560
Three.

137
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,439
I spilled some earlier.

138
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,160
Got any more?

139
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:57,120
That's enough.

140
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,399
Sigh.

141
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,519
A miscalculation.

142
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:05,240
Next time you two come,

143
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,879
I won't bother with any schemes.

144
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:08,040
I'll just kill you outright.

145
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,680
There won't be a next time, Your Highness.

146
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,480
Hey.

147
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:15,079
You want it or not?

148
00:06:15,639 --> 00:06:16,319
Who cares for it?

149
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:22,560
Hey.

150
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,879
Come here, I have something to tell you.

151
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,480
Sigh.

152
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,240
Looks like Ji City was a dead end.

153
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,240
We have to keep moving again.

154
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:37,759
Mm.

155
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:39,160
We're finally rid of Prince Ji.

156
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:40,519
Let's hurry to the next city.

157
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,639
Spit it out.

158
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,800
No tricks.

159
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,839
Actually,

160
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,399
Envoy Qi is the one who least wants you
to marry someone else.

161
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:58,199
Him?

162
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,199
How is that possible?

163
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,720
Ha!

164
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,879
I hit the nail on the head, didn't I?

165
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,160
Told you I could fool you all.

166
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:08,959
Mm-hmm.

167
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,120
To hell with this!

168
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:15,759
Come on, come on, come on.

169
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,319
Here, yours.

170
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,399
Hey.

171
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,360
What are they doing?

172
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:28,680
Oh.

173
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,959
Deleting each other's contact info.

174
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:31,279
They're breaking off their friendship just like that.

175
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:35,240
Their little boat of friendship

176
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,560
just capsized in an instant.

177
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,399
Hey.

178
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,079
Come visit again sometime!

179
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,480
Tch.

180
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,240
Hey, hey!

181
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,480
There's a trap here!

182
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,319
Quick, quick, quick!

183
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:50,399
Come here.

184
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:52,759
Looks like Royal Brother scared you all silly.

185
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,319
It's just a lousy rope.

186
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,480
What's there to be afraid of?

187
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,199
If you won't go, I will.

188
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,920
Uh, ah!

189
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,959
Whoa!

190
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:06,720
Why are you all clapping?

191
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,759
Get me down from here!

192
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:08,439
Hey.

193
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,920
What are you looking at?

194
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:15,279
Ha, I'm still one step ahead of you.

195
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,920
Your friendship is really something.

196
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:21,199
Why is Bai City so far away?

197
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,720
We just can't seem to get there.

198
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,439
Bai City is the farthest from the capital.

199
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,240
It's almost at the border.

200
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,240
Of course it's far.

201
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:30,240
Before we knew it, we'd come this far.

202
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:32,679
And before we knew it, it's the last city.

203
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,919
And you still aren't married off.

204
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,559
Listen to me,

205
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,960
Prince Bai is the last prince left!

206
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:36,879
Ah.

207
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,000
Which means...

208
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:40,799
If Prince Bai doesn't take the throne,

209
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,440
I'll have to ascend the throne myself!

210
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:43,120
Hey.

211
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,679
Which means...

212
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,919
If Prince Bai doesn't marry me,

213
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:49,320
I can't restore my kingdom.

214
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:49,919
Hey.

215
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:53,159
Which means, if Prince Bai
doesn't take the throne,

216
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:53,960
then I'll...

217
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,279
You're not getting away either.

218
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,600
I don't know what you all are talking about,

219
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,559
but Prince Bai sounds pretty important.

220
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,480
Mm.

221
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,879
Run!

222
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:04,639
Old man!

223
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,240
Prince Bai has been killed!

224
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:07,639
Dubian Kingdom is attacking Bai City!

225
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:08,600
Run for your lives!

226
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:21,360
The people of Bai City really all fled.

227
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:24,039
Bai City is so big.

228
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:26,120
There can't be absolutely no one left.

229
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,559
Believe it or not, there is one person.

230
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:35,080
Who are you?

231
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,559
Stop right there!

232
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:40,919
Liu Heng?

233
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:43,639
Royal Brother!

234
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,039
Bookworm!

235
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:44,840
You finally made it!

236
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,279
Any later and I would've died of fright.

237
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:46,960
All right.

238
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,879
Let's just make do here for tonight.

239
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,480
Liu Heng, what are you doing?

240
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:52,440
I heard people say

241
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:55,080
Dubian troops attack here every night.

242
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,279
I don't want to die.

243
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:58,360
I need to save my life to be emperor!

244
00:09:58,759 --> 00:09:59,559
Sigh.

245
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,840
Ouyang Yan's here, what are you scared of?

246
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,360
Good point.

247
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,320
Chicken farmer.

248
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:15,519
Take another careful look.

249
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:16,840
Are there any other princes left?

250
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,320
Prince Nan fell off a cliff.

251
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:22,399
Prince Li, carriage accident.

252
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,039
Prince Yu...

253
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:26,919
crushed to death by his cat in his sleep.

254
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,240
Prince Yang...

255
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:30,159
loved his new scarf so much

256
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,879
he wore it riding and was strangled.

257
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,200
Hey!

258
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,080
Why are you all looking at me?

259
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,879
It wasn't me.

260
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,360
Besides,

261
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:45,200
I, Liu Heng, do have my principles, okay?

262
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:48,200
Killing my brothers isn't my style.

263
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,639
Hey.

264
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,440
What about the other princes?

265
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,840
The others are scattered among the people.

266
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,559
They won't be easy to find anytime soon.

267
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,600
Hey.

268
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,399
How about I sponsor your Daliang Kingdom

269
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,799
and just buy you an emperor?

270
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:04,320
Or just sponsor me to restore my kingdom.

271
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,440
Restore your kingdom?

272
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,039
Crown Prince,

273
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,600
I suggest we head back to the palace first.

274
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,799
That's our only option.

275
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:13,399
General Li and the Grand Scholar
haven't written to me.

276
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,759
I'm a bit worried about the palace.

277
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,320
Then let's set off first thing tomorrow.

278
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:20,320
You all go ahead and sleep first.

279
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:23,799
I've been wanting to write a novel
about a horror inn.

280
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:27,639
But I'm hungry now, so I'll go grab a bite.

281
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:29,240
It's not safe alone. I'll go with you.

282
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:29,799
Hey!

283
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,320
You two have a death wish or something?

284
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,440
The Crown Prince's fanboying is getting kind of scary lately.

285
00:11:36,159 --> 00:11:38,480
You think it's just fanboying for Consort Zhen?

286
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:38,960
What else would it be?

287
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,600
Don't tell me the Crown Prince actually
likes Consort Zhen?

288
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,639
Ah.

289
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:47,320
The Crown Prince really likes Consort Zhen!

290
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,080
Then who does Consort Zhen like?

291
00:11:51,279 --> 00:11:53,799
How can you not understand a girl's heart?

292
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:54,960
You can't even tell?

293
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,000
Liu Heng,

294
00:11:58,639 --> 00:11:59,600
she likes me.

295
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:01,039
Who likes you?

296
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,120
Who's there?

297
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,519
Can't see me, can't see me, can't see me.

298
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,360
What are you doing?

299
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,320
Hey!

300
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,159
You guys aren't even gonna hide?

301
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:12,120
We don't even know if it's a person
or a ghost out there!

302
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,519
Get down first!

303
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,879
Open up, open up, open up!

304
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,120
Who is it?

305
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:19,840
Wait a minute.

306
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:22,639
That sounds like Imperial Uncle Liu's voice.

307
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:23,600
Hold on.

308
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,440
Imperial Uncle went off to attack Dubian Kingdom.

309
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,080
Prince Bai has already died in battle.

310
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,720
So this Imperial Uncle...

311
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,039
Are you stupid?

312
00:12:31,039 --> 00:12:32,320
He's obviously a fake!

313
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,559
Fake, my foot!

314
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,639
Liu Heng,

315
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:37,000
when you were five, you put a snake
in the Empress Dowager's bed,

316
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,639
and got beaten so badly you couldn't stand.

317
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,879
And Crown Prince Liu Le,

318
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:42,120
when you were six, you wet the bed once...

319
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:42,720
Imperial Uncle Liu!

320
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,360
I know it's you now!

321
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,279
I'm opening the door!

322
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,120
Stop laughing!

323
00:12:51,159 --> 00:12:51,960
Imperial Uncle Liu!

324
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,159
Shh!

325
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,159
Someone is after me.

326
00:12:59,159 --> 00:12:59,960
Ah?

327
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,480
Who's trying to kill you?

328
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:04,679
Is it people from Dubian Kingdom?

329
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,600
I don't know.

330
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:09,919
Your Highness,

331
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,840
Prince Bai and I

332
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,039
led the Daliang Kingdom's army

333
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:16,159
and fought Dubian Kingdom's forces
for three days and nights.

334
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:17,840
But...

335
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,840
our Daliang Kingdom's army

336
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:22,360
was completely wiped out.

337
00:13:23,559 --> 00:13:24,360
Prince Bai

338
00:13:25,279 --> 00:13:26,639
also tragically died in battle.

339
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,879
Imperial Uncle,

340
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:31,679
how could Dubian Kingdom be so formidable?

341
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:33,679
I have no idea.

342
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,559
To expand our Daliang Kingdom's borders,

343
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:41,559
has been at war constantly for 20 years.

344
00:13:41,679 --> 00:13:42,799
But Dubian Kingdom

345
00:13:43,399 --> 00:13:45,759
has bided its time for over a decade,

346
00:13:46,279 --> 00:13:47,960
all for this very day!

347
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:50,799
Imperial Uncle,

348
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,519
what do we do now?

349
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,039
Crown Prince,

350
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,320
Crown Prince, don't worry.

351
00:13:57,399 --> 00:13:59,519
Our great Daliang Kingdom

352
00:13:59,559 --> 00:14:00,600
has plenty of military reserves.

353
00:14:01,159 --> 00:14:03,720
Once I return to the capital and redeploy,

354
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:05,799
we'll surely drive back Dubian Kingdom's army.

355
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:07,679
Crown Prince,

356
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:09,159
I suggest we depart immediately.

357
00:14:10,639 --> 00:14:11,440
Hey,

358
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,440
old man, are you alright?

359
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,159
I'm fine.

360
00:14:13,159 --> 00:14:14,080
Just a minor wound.

361
00:14:17,039 --> 00:14:18,159
It's getting late today.

362
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,039
Why don't

363
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,200
we rest here for the night,

364
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,240
and discuss it tomorrow.

365
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:25,559
Then let's rest for tonight.

366
00:14:26,039 --> 00:14:26,960
First thing tomorrow morning,

367
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,120
we'll leave Bai City.

368
00:14:59,480 --> 00:14:59,960
Hmm.

369
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,080
Oh, Imperial Uncle Liu.

370
00:15:02,799 --> 00:15:03,600
Envoy.

371
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,960
Come outside with me.

372
00:15:05,399 --> 00:15:06,600
I have something important

373
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,720
to discuss with you.

374
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:10,559
Imperial Uncle,

375
00:15:10,559 --> 00:15:12,000
what did you call me out here for?

376
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,000
Your Highness.

377
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:16,720
Hey, hey, hey!

378
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,039
Your Highness,

379
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:22,320
all that talk about mobilizing troops was a lie.

380
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,200
I've seen Dubian Kingdom's army.

381
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:27,039
The Dubian Kingdom is terrifying now.

382
00:15:27,159 --> 00:15:28,759
Daliang Kingdom can't possibly win.

383
00:15:28,919 --> 00:15:29,399
Your Highness,

384
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:32,399
please take me back to the Dubian Kingdom.

385
00:15:32,639 --> 00:15:34,480
This old servant will follow you to the death.

386
00:15:34,679 --> 00:15:35,480
Wait, no.

387
00:15:35,799 --> 00:15:36,720
Please, get up first.

388
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,039
What are you talking about?

389
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,960
Oh, Your Highness,

390
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,759
just let me follow you.

391
00:15:42,159 --> 00:15:43,759
The Crown Prince is utterly useless.

392
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,039
My brother, to put him on the throne,

393
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:48,080
drove out all the other princes.

394
00:15:48,639 --> 00:15:50,399
But he just wants to draw comics.

395
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,799
He drove my brother to an early grave.

396
00:15:52,559 --> 00:15:55,240
Daliang Kingdom has been without
an emperor for months.

397
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,279
The people are scattered, in total disarray.

398
00:15:58,159 --> 00:15:59,720
I've completely given up on Daliang Kingdom.

399
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,000
Please, just take me away with you.

400
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:03,559
Your Dubian Kingdom is so prosperous,

401
00:16:04,159 --> 00:16:05,519
the people live and work in contentment,

402
00:16:05,639 --> 00:16:07,039
and the soldiers' morale is sky-high.

403
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,879
Daliang Kingdom is about to be finished.

404
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:11,919
Our Dubian Kingdom...

405
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:12,639
Huh?

406
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,240
Imperial Uncle Liu, what nonsense
are you spouting?

407
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,559
Are you delirious from a fever?

408
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:18,159
No, I don't have a fever.

409
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:20,840
Your Highness,

410
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:24,279
Dubian's victory is already certain.

411
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:26,919
You needn't hide your identity anymore.

412
00:16:26,919 --> 00:16:29,600
Could you stop saying "Dubian Kingdom"?

413
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,200
I have nothing to do with
Dubian Kingdom.

414
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:36,840
It seems you still don't trust my loyalty.

415
00:16:37,639 --> 00:16:39,759
Then I'll just have to prove it to you.

416
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,399
Bring them all out!

417
00:16:42,519 --> 00:16:43,320
Move!

418
00:16:44,879 --> 00:16:45,679
Hurry up!

419
00:16:45,679 --> 00:16:46,320
Move!

420
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,399
Imperial Uncle Liu, what are you doing?

421
00:16:49,399 --> 00:16:50,120
Your Highness,

422
00:16:50,639 --> 00:16:52,279
today I'll kill this useless wretch

423
00:16:52,279 --> 00:16:54,080
and offer you his heart.

424
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:54,759
Imperial Uncle Liu, don't!

425
00:16:54,759 --> 00:16:55,679
The other three

426
00:16:55,679 --> 00:16:56,919
will be a bonus gift.

427
00:16:56,919 --> 00:16:58,320
Imperial Uncle Liu, calm down!

428
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,080
I, I, I...

429
00:16:59,080 --> 00:16:59,679
All right, all right.

430
00:16:59,679 --> 00:17:01,080
Even if I am a Prince of Dubian,

431
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,679
I was born and raised
in Daliang Kingdom.

432
00:17:02,679 --> 00:17:04,839
I have no feelings for Dubian at all!

433
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:05,920
Oh no.

434
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,200
They've all blinded you.

435
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:07,880
This... this...

436
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,640
What's there to miss about Daliang Kingdom?

437
00:17:10,559 --> 00:17:12,400
This useless wretch has ruined it all.

438
00:17:13,519 --> 00:17:14,759
I must kill him today.

439
00:17:14,759 --> 00:17:15,480
Imperial Uncle,

440
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:17,559
I'm just a minor prince.

441
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:19,759
There's no need to trouble yourself
with killing the Crown Prince.

442
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,400
Today, I'll take a gamble.

443
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,400
I'll bet you're the future Emperor of Dubian.

444
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,160
This...

445
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,200
Your Highness,

446
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,039
I want to give you a gift.

447
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:32,759
Choose one of these four to save.

448
00:17:32,839 --> 00:17:33,119
What?

449
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,519
I can't choose.

450
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:48,440
Then I'll kill him first.

451
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:48,920
Wait!

452
00:17:51,319 --> 00:17:52,160
Save Consort Zhen.

453
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:54,880
She's the most innocent one.

454
00:18:01,799 --> 00:18:03,400
But as the imperial envoy,

455
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:04,920
if the Crown Prince comes to harm,

456
00:18:05,519 --> 00:18:07,039
I must end my life in atonement.

457
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:15,720
But if you want to kill her,

458
00:18:16,119 --> 00:18:18,160
you'll have to step over my corpse first.

459
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:18,920
Hahaha!

460
00:18:22,559 --> 00:18:23,359
Oh my.

461
00:18:24,039 --> 00:18:26,920
I thought you were a man of great wisdom,

462
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:28,480
a prince worth following.

463
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:29,720
Who knew

464
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:33,160
you're just a sentimental pretty-boy scholar.

465
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,200
Fine.

466
00:18:35,519 --> 00:18:37,960
Then today, I'll grant you both your wish.

467
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,480
Crown Prince.

468
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,000
Thank you.

469
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:49,039
If it weren't for you,

470
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,799
I'd still be raising chickens in the palace.

471
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,880
These few months serving as your envoy

472
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:56,200
have been my happiest.

473
00:19:00,839 --> 00:19:01,640
Qi Zhi.

474
00:19:02,799 --> 00:19:04,359
I'll ask you one last time.

475
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:06,319
You don't regret it?

476
00:19:06,519 --> 00:19:07,359
No regrets.

477
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:14,079
I don't want to watch her marry
someone else as empress anyway.

478
00:19:19,359 --> 00:19:20,160
Come on.

479
00:19:20,759 --> 00:19:22,400
Let us all die here together.

480
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:23,799
Good.

481
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,000
Very good.

482
00:19:25,319 --> 00:19:26,279
You've passed the test.

483
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:30,480
What test?

484
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,240
Untie them.

485
00:19:33,079 --> 00:19:34,079
T-t-test?

486
00:19:34,599 --> 00:19:35,559
Testing what?

487
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,119
Imperial Uncle Liu, are you insane?

488
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,839
Hahaha!

489
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,240
Oh my.

490
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:42,240
Let me tell you.

491
00:19:42,799 --> 00:19:45,799
Dubian Kingdom was driven off long ago.

492
00:19:45,799 --> 00:19:46,480
What?

493
00:19:47,039 --> 00:19:49,240
When we searched their camp,

494
00:19:49,359 --> 00:19:52,720
we found a torn Dubian royal genealogy.

495
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:55,559
Your name, Qi Zhi, was inside.

496
00:19:56,359 --> 00:19:59,000
To prove you, Qi Zhi, weren't a spy,

497
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,640
we had no choice but to do this.

498
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:01,920
Now it's clear,

499
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:05,359
Dubian Kingdom must have planted it
to turn us against each other.

500
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:07,119
If you don't trust me, just say so.

501
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:08,200
You tested me.

502
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:09,519
Call me overly suspicious this time.

503
00:20:10,319 --> 00:20:13,000
I offer my apologies right here.

504
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:16,240
The Crown Prince and I had to be cautious.

505
00:20:17,119 --> 00:20:18,920
Crown Prince, you knew about this too?

506
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:23,759
Chicken farmer.

507
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:26,480
We did overdo the act just now.

508
00:20:27,119 --> 00:20:27,920
Hey.

509
00:20:28,319 --> 00:20:30,720
But did you really mean it when you thanked me?

510
00:20:31,559 --> 00:20:32,559
Oh, shut up.

511
00:20:33,039 --> 00:20:33,599
Hey.

512
00:20:33,599 --> 00:20:34,319
Qi Zhi.

513
00:20:35,599 --> 00:20:36,400
What?

514
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,279
When Imperial Uncle Liu was about to kill you,

515
00:20:38,279 --> 00:20:39,359
what was it you said?

516
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,799
I said thank you, Crown Prince.

517
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:42,720
No.

518
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,599
The part after that.

519
00:20:47,359 --> 00:20:48,319
Both of you, shut up!

520
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,559
Imperial Uncle Liu.

521
00:20:55,559 --> 00:20:56,240
Is this ever going to end?

522
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,440
One test is enough! How many do you need?

523
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,640
I didn't arrange this one.

524
00:21:21,759 --> 00:21:22,680
We're done for! What do we do?

525
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,519
Imperial Uncle, look out!

526
00:21:58,720 --> 00:21:59,519
Ouyang Que!

527
00:22:21,839 --> 00:22:22,640
Let's go.

528
00:22:27,079 --> 00:22:28,359
Thank you, Young Lord Ouyang, for saving us.

529
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:31,880
Your Highness, Crown Prince.

530
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:34,319
These assassins all serve Eunuch Gao.

531
00:22:34,799 --> 00:22:36,359
Eunuch Gao colluded with the Dubian Kingdom.

532
00:22:36,519 --> 00:22:37,839
He sold out Daliang Kingdom's
military secrets.

533
00:22:38,279 --> 00:22:39,799
And sent men to assassinate the Crown Prince.

534
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,920
The moment I heard the news,

535
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:41,920
I rushed here to protect Your Highness.

536
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,119
Thankfully, I made it in time.

537
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:45,960
That Eunuch Gao.

538
00:22:46,319 --> 00:22:50,039
To think my fourth brother once held him
in such high regard.

539
00:22:51,279 --> 00:22:52,200
Your Highness.

540
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,720
With the throne vacant even for a day,

541
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,759
men like Eunuch Gao will only multiply.

542
00:22:55,759 --> 00:22:57,400
Please, take the throne as soon as possible.

543
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,039
Imperial Uncle Liu.

544
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,039
Please, you take the throne.

545
00:23:04,039 --> 00:23:04,720
Huh?

546
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,039
Imperial Uncle Liu.

547
00:23:06,039 --> 00:23:07,880
You're a brave warrior and a wise ruler.

548
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:08,880
Please, take the throne.

549
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:10,799
I don't agree.

550
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,279
Not that it matters.

551
00:23:17,039 --> 00:23:17,839
Sigh.

552
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:20,400
I'm getting old.

553
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:21,920
Just an old man.

554
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,839
I have no interest in being emperor.

555
00:23:24,079 --> 00:23:25,559
Being emperor

556
00:23:25,559 --> 00:23:26,920
should be left to you young folks.

557
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:27,920
Wonderful, wonderful, wonderful!

558
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:30,960
Imperial Uncle Liu,

559
00:23:31,359 --> 00:23:32,319
there's something you don't know.

560
00:23:32,759 --> 00:23:35,039
We searched for every prince
of Daliang Kingdom.

561
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,839
There's no one left to inherit the throne.

562
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,279
There's still me.

563
00:23:42,319 --> 00:23:43,960
Daliang Kingdom now faces troubles
within and without.

564
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,640
Someone must turn the tide.

565
00:23:46,599 --> 00:23:48,000
Please reconsider, Imperial Uncle.

566
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,000
Very well, then.

567
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:55,480
Tomorrow at dawn,

568
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:56,519
we'll get ourselves ready

569
00:23:56,519 --> 00:23:57,519
and set out immediately

570
00:23:57,799 --> 00:23:58,599
back to the capital,

571
00:23:59,000 --> 00:23:59,799
to take the throne.

572
00:24:02,279 --> 00:24:03,079
Imperial Uncle Liu.

573
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:08,480
Hm?

574
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,039
Then would you

575
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:12,680
make me your empress,

576
00:24:12,839 --> 00:24:13,640
and also

577
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:16,119
not sleep with me?

578
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,039
Don't worry.

579
00:24:20,039 --> 00:24:22,039
The young lord has done a great service in saving us.

580
00:24:22,359 --> 00:24:24,240
Daliang Kingdom will not be ungrateful.

581
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:25,880
Once we return to the capital,

582
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,079
I will surely

583
00:24:27,519 --> 00:24:29,759
grant vast riches and dispatch elite troops

584
00:24:29,839 --> 00:24:30,640
to fully

585
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,200
support your Yan Kingdom.

586
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,279
Oh.

587
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,319
So I don't need to marry you.

588
00:24:36,119 --> 00:24:36,920
Ah.

589
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,200
Thank you, Imperial Uncle Liu.

590
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,200
Tomorrow I'll send men to escort you back.

591
00:24:43,079 --> 00:24:45,039
Then my sister and I will return to Yan.

592
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,119
When you ascend the throne,

593
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,519
we'll come to offer our congratulations.

594
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:51,519
Brother, I'm not leaving.

595
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:54,359
Yan'er.

596
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:56,880
I never wanted you to restore our kingdom
through a political marriage.

597
00:24:57,519 --> 00:24:59,200
Now that Imperial Uncle has shown mercy,

598
00:25:00,079 --> 00:25:01,160
let's just go home.

599
00:25:01,359 --> 00:25:02,599
I'll find you a good husband.

600
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:03,680
No.

601
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,740
I don't want that. I...

602
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:06,799
This isn't up for discussion.

603
00:25:08,519 --> 00:25:09,640
We leave tomorrow.

604
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:12,960
I...

605
00:25:41,079 --> 00:25:41,440
Imperial Uncle.

606
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:42,160
Here.

607
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:54,720
What are you thinking about?

608
00:25:55,119 --> 00:25:56,079
Oh, nothing.

609
00:25:57,519 --> 00:25:58,319
Everyone,

610
00:25:59,599 --> 00:26:01,480
soon I'll be taking my sister back to Yan.

611
00:26:02,519 --> 00:26:03,759
On your way back to the capital,

612
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:05,319
take good care of yourselves.

613
00:26:05,319 --> 00:26:07,079
Why isn't Ouyang Yan down for breakfast?

614
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,000
I don't know.

615
00:26:09,799 --> 00:26:11,920
I knocked on her door this morning
and got no answer.

616
00:26:12,079 --> 00:26:12,920
Forget about her.

617
00:26:13,079 --> 00:26:13,880
Let's just eat.
